      </mappings><SENSE_META clarity=""/>
   </sense>
   <sense group="1" n="4" name="be accountable, responsible (for an
         action/to someone)" type="">
      <commentary>
      </commentary>
      <examples>
         She must answer for her actions.
         I expect parents to answer for their children's behaviour.
         Violence on television has a lot to answer for the violence in
         schools.
         The great thing about working for yourself is that you don't have
         to answer to anyone.
         They will eventually have to answer to the King.
         The Head of the Research Academy answer to the authorities
         empowered to make grants.
      </examples>
